PPSSP_2026.zip

# Large ROOT ntuples/splits are ignored via per-folder .gitignore files inside
# each PPSSP_2026/ tree (see /PPSSP_2026/.gitignore, /Evie/PPSSP_2026/.gitignore,
# /Esteban/PPSSP_2026/.gitignore, /Final_Notebooks/PPSSP_2026/.gitignore) so
# that plots/summary artifacts under those same trees stay tracked.

# Trained model artifacts (XGBoost JSON dumps: final_model_*/model_*_fold*.json,
# features/hyperparams/optuna_features JSON, PyTorch state dicts: model_*_fold*.pt)
# - all fully regenerable by re-running the relevant *_Master_Pipeline.ipynb/
# DNN*.ipynb/MLP*.ipynb (deterministic, seeded), but each retrain produces
# multi-MB non-delta-compressible blobs that previously got committed on every
# run and dominated the repo's git history size (~169MB / 61% of all history
# as of 2026-07-22). Kept on disk but no longer tracked - re-run the owning
# notebook once after a fresh clone if these are missing.
*.json
*.pt

# Per-event OOF score dumps (one row per event across all folds) - these are
# the biggest offenders (41-122MB each, 4 of them tracked as of 2026-07-23),
# unlike the small summary CSVs (run2_vs_run3_auc_summary*.csv,
# model_summary_*.csv, a few KB each) which stay tracked. Regenerable by
# re-running the owning notebook's K-Fold Production Run cell.
oof_scores_*.csv